---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import ProfilePic from '../assets/profile.jpg'; // Replace with your own photo
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="About Gromit's Lab and Mitch"
  pubDate={new Date('2025-06-19')}
>
  <style>
    .about-container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .profile-section {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .profile-section img {
      width: 160px;
      height: 160px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 3px solid #ccc;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .bio {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .bio h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .bio p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: #333;
    }

    section {
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .skills ul {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      list-style-type: disc;
      color: #444;
    }

    .contact {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .contact a {
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      color: #007acc;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: background 0.2s ease;
    }

    .contact a:hover {
      background-color: #e2e2e2;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .profile-section {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .bio h2 {
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }

      .contact {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .contact a {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <div class="profile-section">
  <img src="/images/profile.png" alt="Mitch Profile Photo" />
  <div class="bio">
    <h2>Hi, I'm Mitch</h2>
    <p>
      I'm a Cyber Security Engineer and MSc student in Cyber Security & Digital Forensics, with five years' experience in threat detection, SIEM engineering, and incident response. 
      I started Gromit’s Lab as a digital garden to explore, document, and share open-source tools, research projects, and security techniques I use and build.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="skills">
  <h3>Skills & Focus Areas</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Security Architecture & Cloud Security (Azure / M365)</li>
    <li>Threat Detection, SIEM, Honeypots & Automation</li>
    <li>Digital Forensics & Incident Response</li>
    <li>Python for Security Data Analysis</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h3>My Mission</h3>
  <p>
    I aim to make cybersecurity knowledge more accessible through open documentation, original research, and practical tools. 
    Whether it's automating incident response, decoding authentication protocols, or reverse-engineering forensic traces — 
    I believe in learning by building and sharing.
  </p>
  <p>
    Gromit’s Lab reflects that ethos — a place to prototype, publish, and sometimes play.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <h3>Current Projects</h3>
  <ul class="skills">
    <li><strong>Adaptive Honeypot System</strong> – using MITRE ATT&CK mapping and report generation</li>
    <li><strong>Authentication Protocol Explorer</strong> – visualising handshake flows for MSc blog series</li>
    <li><strong>APT Emulation Platform</strong> – my MSc thesis platform for blue team testbed</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h3>The Lab</h3>
  <p>
    Gromit's Lab isn't a company — it's my personal skunkworks. But every good engineer needs a dogged assistant, 
    and Gromit represents the curiosity, mischief, and love of experimentation that fuels this space.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="contact">
  <h3>Contact & Connect</h3>
  <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mitch-hart-cybersec" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
  <a href="https://github.com/Mitch-Z3JvbWl0" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
  <a href="mailto:mitch@grom-lab.com">Email</a>
</section>

  </div>
</Layout>
